node.detail_zh: 患者過往健康良好，為來自菲律賓的外傭。7 月 10 日乘搭香港航空 HX782 抵港，是首次來港工作，在亞洲國際博覽館檢測後送院，沒有病徵。
node.detail_en: The patient has good past health and is a domestic helper from the Philippines. She arrived in Hong Kong for her first job in Hong Kong by flight HX782 and was hospitalised from AsiaWorld-Expo upon testing positive, having exhibited no symptoms.
